# Title: System Control Panel Item Loaded From Uncommon Location
# Author: Anish Bogati
# Date: 2024-01-09
# Level: high
# Description: Detects image load events of system control panel items (.cpl) from uncommon or non-system locations that may indicate DLL sideloading or other abuse techniques.
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.persistence, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1574.001

ImageLoaded IN ("*\\appwiz.cpl", "*\\bthprops.cpl", "*\\hdwwiz.cpl") NOT (ImageLoaded IN ("C:\\Windows\\Prefetch\\*", "C:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*", "C:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*"))